news.title: FSF Europe newsletter
news.body: Topics: Fellowship portal migrated to eZ publish, Joint Statement of FSFE and FSF Latin America to WIPO GA, WSIS workshop on internet governance and human rights, Workshop about Free Software in Austrian schools, Internet Hungary 2005, Valtellinux in Caiolo (Italy), Internetdagarna in Stockholm (Sweden), FSFE's political message in Ireland, Georg Greve in Brazil, Real Networks leaves antitrust EU case, Microsoft's new "shared source" licenses.
